{"title":"歌唱谢德枚","authors":["李端生"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":10,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌唱谢德枚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"·李端生·"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁水奔流遍地红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跃进年头出英雄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我今不唱别一个，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"单唱煤炭坝一工人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这人名叫谢德枚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生龙活虎正年轻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当上大工才三天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"积极苦干立奇功。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天挖煤十六吨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"超过七级工一倍零。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个个说他效率高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光荣榜上他有名。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他是怎样挖煤的呢？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挖煤就像鸡啄米，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分秒时间不放松，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一锄一锄都带劲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全身力气用得匀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壋头四边挖得好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"架棚没误一点工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼脑手脚齐用上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两天任务一天完成，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三天产量猛上升。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这正是：长江后浪推前浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“子龙”盖过老“黄忠”。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1}